need Blackstar cover from...

19:45.967 --> 19:47.403
Is she okay?

19:47.447 --> 19:50.319
She and Andy broke up.

19:50.363 --> 19:51.277
JILL :
I...

19:51.320 --> 19:53.931
I ruined everything.

19:55.324 --> 19:58.284
What? They were talking, too.

20:00.199 --> 20:01.678
How was the surgery?

20:01.722 --> 20:04.464
I sneezed and got kicked out.

20:04.507 --> 20:06.379
I don't even know
if she made it.

20:06.422 --> 20:08.381
