20:34.581 --> 20:36.191
Forget it.

20:36.235 --> 20:37.366
Tell us everything.

20:37.410 --> 20:38.498
Details, details.

20:38.541 --> 20:40.935
I'm so happy for you.

20:40.978 --> 20:42.284
How was it?

20:42.328 --> 20:44.852
It was like our souls touched.
I kicked out a window.

20:46.680 --> 20:48.943
You don't have to worry
